{"tid":106742,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"係街抄女仔牌狗公啲定交友apps","createTime":"2017-02-04T02:15:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T01:33:12.000Z","uid":16528,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"756d9c9e09f9b9f73de6eabe95c0c4983fc569ba","tid":106742,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T02:15:43.000Z","msg":"一定係街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔知人地有無男朋友<br />\n見過一面之緣就想屌人個閪<br />\n比個假電話又唔撚知醜咁<br />\n死都要打到比人先放人走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n交友apps都係班姣婆想比仔屌<br />\n一個願打一個願挨<br />\n同叫雞一樣<br />\n<br />\n係街抄牌厹啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n交友apps識女厹啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95f38052afcf7b18bcb51dfe4c971acbf8f61389","tid":106742,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T02:18:22.000Z","msg":"why not both"},{"pid":"c457cb21c2113356d10c7bfca22967574553fb3c","tid":106742,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T02:21:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>why not both</blockquote><br />\n玩交友apps既女仔係用性黎換快樂（只限比埋人屌個啲）<br />\n本質同雞一樣<br />\n只係得到既唔係錢咁解"},{"pid":"1810fa64e9a4fc89852753dc63a1ef1e90b74adc","tid":106742,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T02:28:14.000Z","msg":"一句講晒，your face your fate！此post can be closed!"},{"pid":"2de09ff693c1b59dd8f746971ed0aea9a35c342d","tid":106742,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T02:33:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一句講晒，your face your fate！此post can be closed!</blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9605c595b8a99014b5e25a3a95cb1c39beef8d9","tid":106742,"uid":81951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor